import "./ReservationInfo.css" function ReservationInfo(flightInfo) { const originDepartureTime = new Date(flightInfo.flightInfo.departureTime); const destinationArrivalTime = new Date(flightInfo.flightInfo.arrivalTime); var flightDurationMilliseconds = destinationArrivalTime - originDepartureTime; var flightDurationDays = Math.floor(flightDurationMilliseconds / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); return (

Flight ID

{flightInfo.flightInfo.flightID}

Company

{flightInfo.flightInfo.companyName}

From:

{flightInfo.flightInfo.origin}  -  {originDepartureTime.toLocaleString()}

To

{flightInfo.flightInfo.destination}  -  {destinationArrivalTime.toLocaleString()}

Distance

{flightInfo.flightInfo.distance} km

Duration

{flightDurationDays} days

Price

${flightInfo.flightInfo.price}

) } export default ReservationInfo;
